com.codemelon.graph.vertex

Interface EdgeDataVertex<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Vertex
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EdgeColorVertex<E>, EdgeTypeDfsVertex<T>, EdgeTypeVertex<T>, EdgeWeightVertex<T>, KruskalVertex<E>, PrimVertex<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectedDfsVertex, DirectedEdgeDataVertex, UndirectedEdgeDataVertex, UndirectedKruskalVertex, UndirectedPrimVertex

    public interface EdgeDataVertex<T>
extends Vertex
    Specification for vertices supporting edge data. We shouldn't really need a setter here, since access to the pre-existing edge-data object ensures that we can modify the data it contains.
